queries.name: Sales Counters
queries.query: select count(*), sum(payment_value), avg(payment_value), 13.3 as growth, 10 as target from field_demos_retail.payments;

queries.name: Sales per day
Product categories distribution
queries.query:
select sum(price) as amount, product_category_name from field_demos_retail.items i
inner join field_demos_retail.products p on p.product_id = i.product_id  group by product_category_name order by amount desc limit 5;

queries.name: Top resellers
queries.query:
select round(sum(price)) as amount, count(price) as ct, product_category_name from field_demos_retail.items i 
inner join field_demos_retail.products p on p.product_id = i.product_id  group by p.product_category_name order by amount limit 50;

queries.name: Customers - geo repartition
queries.query: select count(*) as customer_count, customer_state from field_demos_retail.customers group by customer_state;

queries.name: Sales per day of week
queries.query:
select sum(payment_value) as weekly_sum, weekofyear(day) as weekofy, concat(dayofweek(day), "-", date_format(day, 'E')) as dayofweek from (
select payment_value, TO_DATE(CAST(UNIX_TIMESTAMP(order_purchase_timestamp, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss') AS TIMESTAMP)) as day from field_demos_retail.payments p
inner join field_demos_retail.orders o on o.order_id = p.order_id  
inner join field_demos_retail.customers c on c.customer_id = o.customer_id ) 
where day > '2018-01-01'
group by weekofy, dayofweek ;
